      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "The LTX-2.3 22B Distilled INT8 inference API is built on a distilled 22-billion parameter model quantized to INT8 precision, reducing memory footprint and accelerating inference without significant accuracy loss. It's designed for production environments where latency and cost are critical. Key attributes include support for standard HTTP endpoints, JSON payloads, and scalable deployment options."
