        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "To integrate the API, start by obtaining API keys from your provider and configuring authentication headers. Use standard HTTP clients like curl or libraries in Python (e.g., requests) to send POST requests to the inference endpoint. Ensure your environment handles JSON serialization and deserialization efficiently. For example:"
